		<div id="overview">
  		<h2>Your fans want to support you.</h2>  
        <!-- <h2>Powered By Super Fans</h2> -->
		<p>Musicians, writers, and creators of all kinds are giving away more and more of their stuff for free. They're building bigger fan bases, but <strong>making a living</strong> is harder than ever.</p>
		<!-- <p><strong><u>The thing is, fans are eager to directly support the things they truly love.</u></strong></p> -->
