           		<h3>New Steady Income</h3>
                <p>We make it simple for your fans to give you money every month. Just a handful of supporters can lead to serious $$$ per month.<br>There's no upfront fees and we take just a small % to cover transaction and administrative fees.</p>
            
            </div>
            
        </div><!-- END LEFT TILE -->
        
        
