        <div id="sub-right">
        
            <div class="sub-inner-right">
            
            	<h3>Big Fans Love It</h3>
                <p>In a time when content is just as easily pirated, true fans take pride in knowing they are helping to support the stuff they love.<br>They have a personal connection to the art and artists and still believe in the craft and the crafters.</p>
                
