        	<h4 class="star">Facebook Page Integration</h4>
            <p>Patrons integrates right into your Facebook Fan Page. No need to worry about another website to keep updated. And your fans are already there!</p>
            
        </div><!-- END LEFT TILE -->
        
        
        <!-- MIDDLE TILE -->
        <div class="feature border">
        
        	<h4 class="credit_card">Hassle Free</h4>
            <p>Accepting credit card payments (and <i>especially</i> recurring payments) can be a huge headache. Don't worry. We handle all that stuff and send you your money once a month.</p>
            
        </div><!-- END MIDDLE TILE -->
    
    
    	<!-- RIGHT TILE -->
        <div class="feature last">
        
        	<h4 class="heart">Know Your Supporters</h4>
